               <objectContents>
                  <ab type="description">Seven women are seated around a table and are socializing. They are watching TV, but do other things as well: reading or smoking. They are seated on chairs, as well as on a long bench next to the wall and curtain. One woman is holding a cigarette and using one of the two ashtrays on the table. Another woman is holding a magasine, whose title is visible - "YU Novosti". Only one woman appear to look to the camera, or more likely to someone who is seated in the direction of the camera. The group of women is oriented towards the TV, and the camera is behind their backs. The TV is placed next to a wall, on a wooden piece of furniture that also holds three plants in pots. The ongoing TV program, the screenshot, shows two men in uniformed clothes and in combat stance, i.e. a sport event in martial arts (probably judo or similar). On the wall behind and aboe the TV, we notice one of the plants, as well as a light and a calendar.</ab>
                  <ab type="comment">Might be irrelevant and can be deleted, but just in case - the 1971 World Judo Championchip took place in Ludwigshafen am Rhein (02-04.IX.1971). </ab>
               </objectContents>
